gujarati.context:
Here is a summary of the Gujarati couplet in English:

The joy of Lord Shri Hari has entered my heart, and with it, extreme happiness has arrived; 

My vital energy has been exhausted, my body has become weak, and I have lost all sense.

transliteration.context:
Here is a summary of the couplet in 1-2 lines:

The eternal Avinash is always present at my doorstep; 
My soul's pain will only end when I become prepared to leave this world.
